{"questionId":"11822","questionHtml":"<p>Solve this system of equations by the eigenvalue method and hence find the general solution for&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>y</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;of the original system.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left| {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {1 - \\lambda }&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;{1 - \\lambda }  \\end{array}} \\right| = 0 \\Rightarrow {\\left( {1 - \\lambda } \\right)^2} - 4 = 0 \\Rightarrow \\lambda = - 1\\,{\\text{or}}\\,3\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>λ</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>λ</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>λ</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>4</mn>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>or</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; M1A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda&nbsp; =&nbsp; - 1\">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  2&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;2  \\end{array}} \\right)\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   q  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   0  \\end{array}} \\right) \\Rightarrow q = - p\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>q</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>q</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;an eigenvector is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda =&nbsp;3\">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  { - 2}&amp;2 \\\\   2&amp;{ - 2}  \\end{array}} \\right)\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  p \\\\   q  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   0  \\end{array}} \\right) \\Rightarrow q = p\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>q</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>q</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;an eigenvector is&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}} 1 \\\\&nbsp; {1}&nbsp; \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; M1A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  X \\\\   Y  \\end{array}} \\right) = A{e^{ - t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) + B{e^{3t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right) \\Rightarrow \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  x \\\\   y  \\end{array}} \\right) = A{e^{ - t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) + B{e^{3t}}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   1  \\end{array}} \\right) + \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {10} \\\\   {20}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n  